data.description: Welcome to the heart of the Villas of West End! This exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhome, constructed in 2016, is a vision of contemporary elegance spanning 1,696 square feet. Upon entering, you'll be captivated by the seamless open-concept layout that effortlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek cabinetry, soft-close cabinets/drawers, stainless steel appliances, and a convenient breakfast bar – an ideal setting for entertaining or enjoying casual meals. Bathed in natural light, the living room creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, great for moments of relaxation. Your master bedroom awaits as a true sanctuary, offering generous space, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom. The two additional bedrooms are thoughtfully designed and share a well-appointed second bathroom. Whether you're a growing family or an avid host, this townhome effortlessly caters to your lifestyle. Step outside to your serene screened patio, a tranquil haven for morning coffees or evening gatherings. The Villas of West End community exudes serenity with meticulously maintained landscaping and a strong sense of community. Parking is a breeze with your own two-car garage. Location takes center stage, placing you directly across the street from The Town of Tioga, where shopping, dining, and entertainment options abound. Seize the opportunity to transform this into your home sweet home. Schedule a showing today and embark on the ultimate townhome living experience at the Villas of West End!
